    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to level 1 per the MRL 2 assessment plan for a Class II CPB device. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Decision: Accepted for the intended regulatory submission supporting 510(k) clearance.",
